	<ul id="todo-list">
		<li>Warm-up (5-10 minutes)
			<input type="checkbox" id="warm-up" />
			<label for="warm-up">Done</label>
		</li>
		<li>Monday (Upper Body Workout)
			<input type="checkbox" id="monday-workout" />
			<label for="monday-workout">Done</label>
			<ul>
				<li>Push-ups: 3 sets of 12 reps</li>
				<li>Tricep dips: 3 sets of 12 reps</li>
				<li>Bicycle crunches: 3 sets of 12 reps</li>
				<li>Arm circles: 3 sets of 12 reps</li>
				<li>Plank hold: 3 sets of 30-second hold</li>
			</ul>
		</li>
		<li>Tuesday (Lower Body Workout)
